      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay, interveinal chlorosis. i havent heard that term before. so if it is the ph, what range should i be aiming for with blueberries? and is there anything i should look for in the soil itself, like texture or stuff under the surface, that would hint at why the nutrients aren't reaching the plant?",
