    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "makes sense. i'll try to fix the drainage. i was also wondering, if i dig down a bit to check the roots, is there anything else common i'd see down there? like specific types of organic matter or maybe even little tunnels or disruptions in the dirt that would tell me if something's wrong with the soil structure?",
